info.author: Maarten van Gompel
classifiers: License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v3 (GPLv3)
info.keywords: nlp computational_linguistics frequency ngram skipgram pmi cooccurrence linguistics
info.name: colibricore
info.summary: Colibri core is an NLP tool as well as a C++ and Python library for working with basic linguistic constructions such as n-grams and skipgrams (i.e patterns with one or more gaps, either of fixed or dynamic size) in a quick and memory-efficient way. At the core is the tool ``colibri-patternmodeller`` which allows you to build, view, manipulate and query pattern models.
